#       - Authentication & Registration | Login is possible with email or username which will used for login into World of Warcraft
#       - Accountcenter | Possibility for users to edit accuont data like username, password recovery, account locking, ect.
#       - Arsenal | A basic and smart viewable armory to watch characters of every realm.
#       - Vote Reward | A system to give ingame rewards to players for voting points
